                    p Minerva Model UN is an emerging foundation which has its roots in the vision of some students from grades 11 and 12. This chapter, very much like the previous one is an Online conference, keeping in mind the current situation around the globe. To recapitulate things, the first chapter was a grand success for all of us with the participation of over 200 delegates from India as well as many other countries and building upon that, we are expecting over 500 delegates for the Second chapter.
                    br
                    p Apart from our conferences, we are proud to have received a Letter of Recommendation from the Governor of Gujarat, honourable Sri Acharya Devvrat, the Governor of Meghalaya, honourable Sri Satya Pal Malik and the honourable Chief Minister of Rajasthan Shri Ashok Gehlot. Our organisation is recognised by the United Nations General Assembly (UNGA) and we also have successful ties with NGOs like the Abraham Lincoln Shiksha Society, etc.
