                    p 5. Dr Kalyan Srinivas Raygalla &#91; Prominent Entrepreneur &#93;
                    p 6. Dr Sudhakar  &#91; Famous Psychologist &#93;
                    p 7. Amb. K.P. Fabian &#91; former ambassador to Qatar and Italy &#93;
                    br
                    p Inspired by the Atmanirbhar approach introduced by our government, we too have developed our strategies and ideologies. We host committees of a great spectrum ranging from a future crisis like dealing with the galactic federation to the past like the Reagan Administration idea of Star Wars, we also support human rights of prisoners that are being violated to a high extent by a lot of countries in the contemporary world and we also are revisiting the Indian elections of 2019 to develop the spirit of a true politician amongst the delegates and we also have a journalists committee, that is to support the fourth pillar of democracy.

